instruction: Generate a resume with data-driven insights
input:
Name: John Smith 
Experience: 5 years as a software engineer
output:
John Smith

Software Engineer

EXPERIENCE

• 5+ years of experience as a software engineer, specializing in web, mobile and desktop application development
• Experienced in developing and deploying software solutions using a variety of programming languages and frameworks, and utilizing Design Patterns
• Skilled in software development life cycle, from identifying customer and business requirements to implementation, maintenance and support
• Effective in developing and managing databases, working on different platforms, and maintaining the highest level of quality assurance
• Proven track record of meeting customer requirements and delivering successful projects on time, within budget and within agreed set of processes
• Expertise in developing and optimizing algorithms, coding, debugging and problem-solving techniques
• Robust experience in developing software solutions that meet and exceed client expectations 
• Self-motivated, with strong work ethic, leadership and organizational skills


EDUCATION 

• Bachelor of Science in Computer Science, University of California, San Diego
• Certified Scrum Master, Scrum Alliance 
• Project Management Professional, Project Management Institute
